will be let loose. </div><div class="t m1863 xbd h4 y17ce ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The whole world will be involved in ruin more terrible than </div><div class="t me1e xbd h4 y246 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that which came upon Jerusalem of </div><div class="t m126 x52 h30 y246 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">old.&quot;—&quot;The Great Con-</div><div class="t m2a5 xbd h30 y1996 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">troversy,&quot; page 614. </div><div class="t m45e x29 h3e y1c38 ff4 fs17 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Count your Sabbath school offerings </div><div class="t m91b x29 h3e y1860 ff4 fs17 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">given so far this quarter. Note how </div><div class="t m1355 x29 h3e y26b ff4 fs17 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">far short you are of reaching the goal </div><div class="t m9e2 x29 h3e y68e ff4 fs17 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the quarter. Make up the lack </div><div class="t mf1 x3f h3e y1cd8 ff4 fs17 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">on the thirteenth Sabbath. </div><div class="t m5c3 x29 h3e y6b1 ff4 fs17 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Thirteenth Sabbath Offering is </div><div class="t me0d x29 h3e y1a37 ff4 fs17 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for establishing Training Schools for </div><div class="t m33e x29 h3e y1cc2 ff4 fs17 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Colored in the Home Field and in </div><div class="t mcfd x51 h3e y1ac7 ff4 fs17 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mission Lands. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
